OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774627872
OL,3,CJust Eat and Autotrader among
OL,4,Ccompanies under investigation over
OL,5,Cfake reviews
OL,7,FThe UK competition watchdog has
OL,8,Flaunched investigations into five
OL,9,Fcompanies, including food delivery
OL,10,Fservice Just Eat and online automotive
OL,11,Fmarketplace Autotrader, as part of a
OL,12,Fcrackdown on fake and misleading
OL,13,Freviews.
OL,15,FThe Competition and Markets Authority
OL,16,F(CMA) is also investigating funeral
OL,17,Fbusiness Dignity, restaurant Pasta
OL,18,FEvangelists and Feefo, a reviews site
OL,19,Fcollecting customer ratings of various
OL,20,Fcompanies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774627872
OL,3,CJust Eat and Autotrader among
OL,4,Ccompanies under investigation over
OL,5,Cfake reviews
OL,7,FWhile the investigations focus on
OL,8,Fdifferent areas, the aim is to see if
OL,9,Fthey have broken consumer law.
OL,11,FFood delivery service Just Eat is
OL,12,Fbeing looked into over claims that the
OL,13,Fcompany's rating system has inflated
OL,14,Fparticular establishments star ratings.
OL,16,FMeanwhile, Autotrader and Feefo are
OL,17,Funder investigation to see whether a
OL,18,Fnumber of 1-star reviews, moderated by
OL,19,FFeefo, were not published on
OL,20,FAutotrader's platform.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774627872
OL,3,CJust Eat and Autotrader among
OL,4,Ccompanies under investigation over
OL,5,Cfake reviews
OL,7,FDignity is under a microscope for
OL,8,Fallegedly asking staff to write
OL,9,Fpositive reviews, while investigators
OL,10,Fsay Pasta Evangelists may have offered
OL,11,Fcustomers discounts on future orders,
OL,12,Fin exchange for leaving 5-star reviews.
OL,14,FWhile the CMA is investigating these
OL,15,Ffive businesses, it has not reached
OL,16,Fany conclusions about whether consumer
OL,17,Flaw has been broken.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
