FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774627872
OL,3,CJust Eat and Autotrader among
OL,4,Ccompanies under investigation over
OL,5,Cfake reviews
OL,7,FSarah Cardell, chief executive of the
OL,8,FCMA, said: "Fake reviews strike at the
OL,9,Fheart of consumer trust ` with many of
OL,10,Fus worrying about misleading content
OL,11,Fwhen looking at reviews online.
OL,13,F"With household budgets under
OL,14,Fpressure, people need to know they're
OL,15,Fgetting genuine information ` not
OL,16,Freviews or star-ratings that have been
OL,17,Fmanipulated to push them towards the
OL,18,Fwrong choice.
OL,26,@pD@LOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
