FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774627872
OL,3,CJust Eat and Autotrader among
OL,4,Ccompanies under investigation over
OL,5,Cfake reviews
OL,7,F"We've given businesses the time to
OL,8,Fget things right. Now we're deploying
OL,9,Four new powers to tackle some of the
OL,10,Fmost harmful practices head on."
OL,12,FWhich? Research found that 89% of UK
OL,13,Fadults said they use online customer
OL,14,Freviews when researching a product or
OL,15,Fservice.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@`O]
