OL,3,CJust Eat and Autotrader among
OL,4,Ccompanies under investigation over
OL,5,Cfake reviews
OL,7,FThe investigations bring the total
OL,8,Fnumber of businesses under review
OL,9,Fusing the CMA's new consumer powers to
OL,10,F14.
OL,12,FIf the CMA finds an infringement of
OL,13,Fthe law, it can require businesses to
OL,14,Fchange their practices and impose
OL,15,Ffines of up to 10% of global turnover.
OL,17,FWhat have the companies under
OL,18,Finvestigation said?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
