PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774627872
OL,3,CJust Eat and Autotrader among
OL,4,Ccompanies under investigation over
OL,5,Cfake reviews
OL,7,FAll five companies have all said that
OL,8,Fthey are cooperating with the CMAs
OL,9,Fongoing investigations.
OL,11,FJust Eat said: "We are working closely
OL,12,Fwith the CMA to ensure the reviews and
OL,13,Fratings on our platform are clear,
OL,14,Ftransparent and easy to use for all
OL,15,Four customers and partners."
OL,17,FIt added that its "goal has always
OL,18,Fbeen to create a platform that works
OL,19,Ffor everyone".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
