CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774627872
OL,3,CJust Eat and Autotrader among
OL,4,Ccompanies under investigation over
OL,5,Cfake reviews
OL,7,FAutotrader said: "We endeavour always
OL,8,Fto operate as a responsible and
OL,9,Fcompliant business and will cooperate
OL,10,Ffully with the CMA's investigation."
OL,12,FDignity said it takes the CMA's
OL,13,Fconcerns "extremely seriously and are
OL,14,Ffully cooperating with its
OL,15,Finvestigation relating to the
OL,16,FCrematorium and Memorial Group (CMG)"
OL,17,F, a business division within its group.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
