CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774627872
OL,3,CJust Eat and Autotrader among
OL,4,Ccompanies under investigation over
OL,5,Cfake reviews
OL,7,FThe business added: "We are committed
OL,8,Fto ensuring full compliance with
OL,9,Fconsumer law and will continue to
OL,10,Fengage constructively with the CMA
OL,11,Fthroughout this process."
OL,13,FPasta Pasta Evangelists said it is
OL,14,Falso "cooperating fully with the CMA",
OL,15,Fsaying: "We take the integrity and
OL,16,Ftransparency of customer reviews
OL,17,Fextremely seriously and are committed
OL,18,Fto ensuring that our practices are
OL,19,Ffully compliant with consumer law."
OL,21,FTips for spotting fake reviews
